&quot;center&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;en&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>;不幸的消息，Juno for YouTube 已从 App Store 中删除。构建起来充满乐趣，感谢所有使用它并享受它的人！ ❤️ &lt;a href=&quot;https://t.co/W1xLBpKSgd&quot;>;https://t.co/W1xLBpKSgd&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>;—克里斯蒂安·塞利格 (@ChristianSelig)...&lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/ div>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259784/juno-youtube-apple-vision-pro-app-removed-christian-selig&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip; &lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259784/juno-youtube-apple-vision-pro-app-removed-christian-selig" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259784/juno-youtube-apple-vision-pro-app-removed-christian-selig</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T18:12:43-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T18:12:43-04:00</updated><title>据报道，任天堂已经关闭了 Ryujinx，据说可以免疫的 Switch 模拟器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;黑红任天堂标志&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ANm-VmStN4eCwIS8ejigYu7h9G0=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn. com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73625399/acastro_200729_1777_nintendo_0001.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;由 Alex Castro / The Verge 绘制的插图&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;uxnoiz&quot;>;任天堂可能刚刚赢得了一场让最受欢迎的 Nintendo Switch 模拟器破产的战斗。 3 月份，&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/3/4/24090357/nintendo-yuzu-emulator-lawsuit-settlement&quot;>;起诉 Yuzu 使其不复存在&lt;/a>;——现在它可能说服了 Yuzu 的主要竞争对手 Ryujinx 也离开了。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;I1W1wM&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://ryujinx.org/download&quot;>;Ryujinx 的下载页面&lt;/a>;现在是空的。 &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/Ryujinx/&quot;>;它的 GitHub&lt;/a>; 已经消失了。模拟器的 &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/RyujinxEmu/status/1841188744126480428&quot;>;X 社交媒体页面&lt;/a>; 和官方 Discord 现在包含一个可能的解释：任天堂联系了其首席开发人员，并说服了他们永久关闭该项目。&lt;/p>; &lt;div id=&quot;qq7DYV&quot;>; &lt;blockquote class=&quot;twitter-tweet&quot;>; &lt;p lang=&quot;zxx&quot; dir=&quot;ltr&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https: //t.co/2Ggt9SWoDI&quot;>;pic.twitter.com/2Ggt9SWoDI&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>;— Ryujinx (@RyujinxEmu) &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/RyujinxEmu/status/1841188744126480428?ref_src =twsrc%5Etfw&quot;>;2024 年 10 月 1 日&lt;/a>; &lt;/blockquote>; &lt;/div>; &lt;p id=&quot;0ZXSXB&quot;>;“昨天，任天堂联系了 gdkchan，并表示同意停止该项目的工作，删除他控制的组织和所有相关资产，”开发者和版主写道...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259791/nintendo -ryujinx-switch-emulator-gdkchan-removed-downloads-github&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259791/nintendo-ryujinx-switch-emulator-gdkchan-removed-downloads-github" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/10/1/24259791/nintendo-ryujinx-switch-emulator-gdkchan-removed-downloads-github</id><author><name>肖恩·霍利斯特</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T18:10:42-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T18:10:42-04:00</updated><title>您现在可以购买的最好的即时相机</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/uLwBnCI-VbdGdcrxgmSG_CrADWo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image /71015667/236751_Instant_Camera_Buying_Guide.7.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Kristen Radtke / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;我们找到了最适合您的预算和需求的相机。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/23133103/best-instant-cameras-fujifilm-polroid-kodak&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23133103/best-instant-cameras-fujifilm-polaroid-kodak" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23133103/best-instant-cameras-fujifilm-polroid-kodak</id><author><name>希娜·瓦萨尼</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-10-01T17:01:28-04:00</published><updated> 2024-10-01T17:01:28-04:00</updated><title>下一代 iPhone SE 可能会失去 home 键，添加 Face ID 和 Apple Intelligence</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;直立放在桌子上的 iPhone 14。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/T6Y32Q-Wlup_D3jDuqIks4Ozwkg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73625220/226270_IPHONE_14_REGULAR_PHO_阿克拉莱斯_0657.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;iPhone 14，下一代 iPhone SE 可能看起来很像。&lt;/em>; |摄影：Amelia Holowaty Krales / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;EtL48V&quot;>;一款感觉非常像任何其他现代非预算 iPhone 的 iPhone SE 显然将于明年初推出，&lt;a href =&quot;https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-01/apple-readies-iphone-se-4-upgraded-ipad-air-for-early-2025&quot;>;根据&lt;em>;彭博社&lt;/em>;的马克·古尔曼&lt;/a>;。该手机将使用 Face ID，并且能够运行 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/6/10/24175405/wwdc-apple-ai-news-features-ios-18-macos -15-iphone-ipad-mac&quot;>;Apple Intelligence&lt;/a>;，他今天重申。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;5hwHsF&quot;>;新款 iPhone SE 型号可能支持 Apple Intelligence &lt;a href=&quot;https: //www.theverge.com/2024/8/11/24217924/iphone-se-apple-intelligence-support-generative-ai-rumor&quot;>;说了很多关于他们的表现&lt;/a>; - 这需要&lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/12/24219823/apple-intelligence-gemini-copilot-ai-iphone-16-pro-pixel-9-ram&quot;>;大量内存&lt;/a>;例如，运行本地人工智能功能。预计它们看起来会像 iPhone 14，取消厚实的顶部和底部边框以及主页按钮；两者都是入门级智能手机的首创。还有传言称 iPhone SE 4 将&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/3/24234749/apple-iphone-se-4th- Generation-oled-display-rumor-leak&quot; >;获取 OLED 屏幕&lt;/a>;，而不是通常的 LCD。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;9Pu3LU&quot;>;&lt;div data-anthem -component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;Apple 的下一代 iPhone SE 可能会升级 OLED&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge .com/2024/9/3/24234749/apple-iphone-se-4th- Generation-oled-display-rumor-leak&quot;},{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;下一代 iPhone SE 可能拥有 Apple Intelligence，这说明了很多&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/8/11/24217924/iphone-se-apple-intelligence-support-generative-ai-rumo